de.pifpafpuf.web.urlparam

Interface ParamCodec<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanCodec, DateCodec, EnumCodec, IntegerCodec, IsoMonthCodec, StringCodec

    public interface ParamCodec<E>
    encodes and decodes values from and to a string form. The string form must be uniquely decodable back in to the value.

    • Method Summary
